      <title>泰森食品预计 2025 年鸡肉业务盈利将增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/chicken-turnaround-prompts-tyson-to-forecast-better-year-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰森食品公司表示，预计明年业绩将有所改善，因为鸡肉业务的好转和预制食品需求的增加抵消了牛肉业务的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/chicken-turnaround-prompts-tyson-to-forecast-better-year-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 12:31:11 GMT</pubDate>
